{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you had the star they could easily see that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and then later on they came and picked up the people what they had the list of and went to the houses.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So tell us what happened to your family at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, um, I remember some of the relatives being picked up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where I lived in Amsterdam, we had a square.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where they had kind of-- more or less, they gathered them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had the trucks there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, uh, I have seen a couple of my uncles and aunts being put on transports right there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was nothing you could do, of course, well, you know, German have weapons, and all this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, you know, I know-- I know a couple uncles and aunts who were picked up, picked out of the houses, with my nieces and that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were from there transported to the downtown in Amsterdam from where they put on transport to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Gradually, you know, the family when that started-- and there's another thing, we-- where we lived we had an attic where we had, we thought, we could hide-- some hiding places for.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my uncles and aunts and all this, they started to bring their silverware, and all the jewelry, and all this what they have.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They brought them over to be put up in the attic there in the places.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I know my grandparents brought stuff, my uncles, my aunts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, you know, we had quite a bit of-- put down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was all behind boards and walls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then coming back after the war to that house there was nothing left, already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Somewhere along the line the neighbors must have-- they knew about it, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
